- Distance: 11.9 km
- [Strava](https://www.strava.com/activities/12317795674)

Paul, Kev, Claire, Cath, Mark and Gordon with
Dave setting off a little late and meeting us on the water. 

It was gentle turning the corner around the pier with not much swell and the wind behind our backs.

No surf at Longsands, but it was high enough tide to paddle through the Cullercoats arch and even into Table Rocks pool

Tide was ebbing as we came back around the piers which meant a little effort was needed to get back into the mouth. 

We put a little speed on for the sprint along the wall and back into the Haven just as it was getting dark.
